observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor comply with the quarterly remittance of RPT/SET shares of barangays and to the Province.

We also recommended that the Municipal Accountant:

Review RPT/SET collections of prior years up to CY 2019 to determine the shares of each Barangay of LGU-Naval and the Provincial share;

Prepare immediately the Disbursement Vouchers for the release of  prior years’ payables on RPT/SET shares to the recipient barangays and to the Province; 

Prepare a monthly schedule showing the amount of the RPT/SET payable to the Province and each barangay and record in individual subsidiary ledger; and

Prepare, within five (5) days after the end of each quarter, the Disbursement Vouchers for the release of the RPT/SET shares to the recipient barangays and to the Province, without need for demand.
